<section id='UpdateStyles'>
<title>UpdateStyles</title>

<command>
<cmdsynopsis>
	<arg choice='plain'>UpdateStyles</arg>
</cmdsynopsis>
</command>

<para>All pending updates of all windows' styles and looks are applied
immediately.  E.g. if
<fvwmref cmd="Style"/>,
<fvwmref cmd="Style" opt="WindowStyle"/> or
<fvwmref cmd="Style" opt="TitleStyle"/>
commands were issued inside a fvwm function.</para>

</section>
